  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multi-agent architecture with Tree of Attacks (TAP) exploration",
    "Modern attack techniques including Crescendo, Many-Shot, Chain-of-Thought Hijacking",
    "TombRaider pattern for defense fingerprinting and exploitation",
    "Dual scan modes for system prompt extraction and prompt injection testing",
    "Configurable models for attacker, target, and evaluator agents",
    "Research-backed techniques incorporating CVE-documented vulnerabilities",
    "Comprehensive probe library with 100+ attack templates",
    "CLI and programmatic API interfaces"
  ],
